  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.header": "苦力怕爆破室 搭建",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_1": "结构支持3种尺寸",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_2": "结构顶面中心需为动力冲压机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_3": "结构底面中心需为生物打包机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_4": "结构的框架由防爆机壳搭成",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_5": "除了顶面和底面的任意面中心可以被替换为防爆玻璃",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_6": "除此之外，每个结构还必须包括一个爆破室核心",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_7": "以及两个任意大小的防爆保险库（连接的保险库算做一个）",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_8": "结构成型以后，顶面的棱会被自动替换为链式传动箱",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_10040.text_9": "使用扳手可以在机壳和传动箱之间切换，但是需要保证能够剩下的传动箱足以驱动所有冲压机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_2c227.header": "苦力怕爆破室 过载",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_2c227.text_1": "苦力怕爆破室最高接受128rpm的转速",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_2c227.text_2": "超过128rpm的转速会使其进入过载状态",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_2c227.text_3": "不要长时间过载，除非你想引起一次足以炸毁你基地的大爆炸！",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_a77f7.header": "苦力怕爆破室 高压聚爆",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_a77f7.text_1": "向爆破室中输入高压苦力怕...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_a77f7.text_2": "可以将配方调整为“高压聚爆”模式",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_a77f7.text_3": "“高压聚爆”模式有单独的配方，不再执行粉碎配方",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_a77f7.text_4": "当然，过载引起的爆炸烈度也会成倍增加",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.header": "苦力怕爆破室 运作",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.text_1": "爆炸室核心可以通过纸箱输入和输出苦力怕",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.text_2": "最大的爆破室最多可以有9个苦力怕同时工作",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.text_3": "通入应力...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.text_4": "每有一只苦力怕，爆破室就会提取输入保险库中的一组物品，执行粉碎轮的粉碎配方，输出到输出保险库",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_s_c38b1.text_5": "右键长按保险库可以调整其为输入或输出",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_scene_1.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_scene_1.text_1": "Edit this ponder scene!",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_scene_1.text_2": "它可以高效批量地执行粉碎配方",
  "create_biotech.ponder.creeper_blast_chamber_scene_1.text_3": "或者...你想来点更劲爆的？",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bone_ratchet.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bone_ratchet.text_1": "骨质棘轮只接受一种方向的旋转",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bone_ratchet.text_2": "接受反方向应力时，他会卡死整个应力网络",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_s_8911d.header": "唤魔者附魔室",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_s_8911d.text_1": "这是唤魔者附魔室",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_s_8911d.text_2": "它可以将附魔书（复印本）附魔为可以使用的附魔书",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_s_8911d.text_3": "通过经验泵向其输送附魔所需要的经验",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_s_8911d.text_4": "附魔书的总等级越高，所需的经验越多，时间越长",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.text_1": "这是一个简单的附魔流水线",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.text_2": "这是鱿鱼打印机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.text_3": "在侧面标记一本附魔书...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.text_4": "它会将下方的书加工为附魔书（复印本）",
  "create_biotech.ponder.evoker_enchanting_chamber_scene_1.text_5": "无论是否在工作，打印机都需要输入水来保证鱿鱼存活",
  "create_biotech.ponder.magma_belt_connector.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.magma_belt_connector.text_1": "使用鼓风机烧炼物品比较占空间",
  "create_biotech.ponder.magma_belt_connector.text_2": "使用岩浆怪传送带",
  "create_biotech.ponder.magma_belt_connector.text_3": "它会自动烧炼其上方的物品，所需时间与鼓风机相同",
  "create_biotech.ponder.magma_belt_connector.text_4": "它没有鼓风机的烧炼保护，记得在它被第二次燃烧前把它取走！",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_clutch.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_clutch.text_1": "史莱姆离合器会在输入应力不支持驱动整个应力网络时自动断开，而不影响网络的其他部分",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_clutch.text_2": "并在应力充足时自动恢复",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.header": "唤魔者附魔室",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_1": "这是唤魔者附魔室",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_2": "它可以将附魔书（复印本）附魔为可以使用的附魔书",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_3": "通过经验泵向其输送附魔所需要的经验",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_4": "附魔书的总等级越高，所需的经验越多，时间越长",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_1": "这是一个简单的附魔流水线",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_2": "这是鱿鱼打印机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_3": "在侧面标记一本附魔书...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_4": "它会将下方的书加工为附魔书（复印本）",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_5": "无论是否在工作，打印机都需要输入水来保证鱿鱼存活",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.text_1": "史莱姆万向节可以在相近的任意两个点之间传播应力",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.text_2": "以一个节点为中心，另一个节点需要在5×5×5范围内",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.header": "经验泵 输出",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_1": "输出端在没有阻塞时会输出经验球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_2": "也可以输出到经验储罐，或其他接受经验的容器",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_3": "输出端不能直接将经验转化为物品",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_4": "你需要将经验通入经验母岩...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_5": "催化成熟的经验簇会自然掉落，它存储的经验值远高于经验颗粒",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.header": "Scene 1",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_1": "经验泵可以用于在泵两端传递经验",
